"""
        Test that an InvalidField error is raised when a GetAttributeList
        response payload is written to a data stream with no attribute names.
        """
payload = payloads.GetAttributeListResponsePayload(self.unique_identifier, None
    )
args = utils.BytearrayStream(),
self.assertRaisesRegex(exceptions.InvalidField,
    'The GetAttributeList response payload is missing the attribute names field.'
    , payload.write, *args)
